Package com.complexible.common.primitives

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LongIterator
    An iterator over primitive longs
    LongIteratorEx<E extends Throwable>
    An iterator over longs which is parameterized by an exception type
    Serializers.ObjectSerializer<T>
    Generic serializer interface for objects.
    SkippingLongIteratorEx<E extends Throwable>
    Similar to SkippingLongIterator but allows for exception specification.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractLongIteratorEx<T extends Throwable>
    A skeleton implementation of LongIteratorEx allowing subclasses to concentrate of computing next elements.
    ArrayUtil
    Bits
    Utility class for manipulating bits
    ConstantAppendingLongIterator<T extends Throwable>
    This is a union of a long iterator with a constant.
    LongIteratorEx.EmptyLongIteratorEx<E extends Throwable>  
    Serializers
    Provides support for serializing/deserializing object or primitive values to/from byte arrays.
    Serializers.IntSerializer
    Serializer for primitive integer values.
    Serializers.LongSerializer
    Serializes the given long to 8 bytes.
    Serializers.ShortSerializer
    Serializes the given short to 2 bytes.
    Serializers.VarLongSerializer
    Serializes the given long to as many bytes as required.
